{"tid":1528280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[飛機迷] 機場附近可唔可以玩航拍？","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T13:33:03.000Z","uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69e961e0a76d19811cc22d8ec2c50fc3c9df3498","tid":1528280,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:29:17.000Z","msg":"去外國旅遊嘅時候，想影下啲飛機升降。要距離幾遠先安全㗎？"},{"pid":"cb1a91d2aa2a6c2512e6d068dff9b454f968b6f3","tid":1528280,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"但我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2174233b5f28b40149a20a1daf33de86228b4ab5","tid":1528280,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658e84dfe2d011eeeaa53b9e7912db39045dac84","tid":1528280,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2651f1af6bde26a1f6811c100c0b7e2befcbe1c0","tid":1528280,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e53566992f5529903cd73ce0c7f34bf88280534","tid":1528280,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f58ec7875ed3b4c43558324aab08f97ae74e87","tid":1528280,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6480298c867770c0a896b8a084b5ef90fa15ffc","tid":1528280,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"民航處訂定了「無線電控制模型飛機飛行安全指引」，供公眾參考。該指引適用於不超過７千克（不計燃料）作消閒用途的無人機。有關指引提醒市民不應在機場及飛機升降航道範圍附近放飛無人機。此外，無人機的飛行地點，必須遠離建築物、人群及直升機坪，以及一切可干擾無線電信息的電源，例如電線、變壓站、高壓電線和變壓塔等，並且必須讓操作者視野清晰無阻，及能夠清楚看見飛行中的無人機，以免發生碰撞導致他人受傷、死亡，或造成財物損失。"}]}